pr_title: Adding Three New Date Prompts for ODK-X Survey
pr_body: Date prompts added for review include year only, month only, and month and year only.
pr_review_comments:
[{'comment_id': 653304861, 'comment_body': 'I think the previous code you had here might be better. It looks like `year()` returns a number whereas `format('YYYY')` was a string

```
> moment('2000-07-01').format('YYYY')
"2000"

> moment('2000-07-01').year()
2000
```

This will probably work most (maybe all?) of the time anyway because of Javascript type coercion though, so not that important to change it', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2021, 6, 17, 7, 35, 11, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'albertchae', 'type': 'User'}, {'comment_id': 653306439, 'comment_body': 'I think this one is more important than year to use format

```
> moment('2000-07-01').format('MM')
"07"

> moment('2000-07-01').month()
6
```

So it's confusing both because it doesn't pad to 2 digits automatically and also appears to 0-index years so that January is 0 and July is 6', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2021, 6, 17, 7, 37, 25, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'albertchae', 'type': 'User'}]

pr_title: Adding 12 Non-Gregorian Calendar Date Prompts for ODK-X Survey
pr_body:
The non-Gregorian calendars added to ODK-X Survey include:

- Coptic Calendar
- Ethiopian Calendar
- Hebrew Calendar
- Islamic Calendar
- Julian Calendar
- Mayan Calendar
- Nanakshahi Calendar
- Nepali (Bikram Sambat) Calendar
- Persian Calendar
- Taiwan Calendar
- Thai Calendar
- Umm Al-Qura Calendar
